description: Concludes a multipart upload once you have uploaded all the components.

parameters.name: sequenceStoreId
parameters.description: The sequence store ID for the store involved in the multipart upload.

parameters.name: uploadId
parameters.description: The ID for the multipart upload.

parameters.name: parts
parameters.description: The individual uploads or parts of a multipart upload. (dict) --- Part of the response to the CompleteReadSetUpload API, including metadata. A number identifying the part in a read set upload. The source file of the part being uploaded. A unique identifier used to confirm that parts are being added to the correct upload.

nested_params.name: partNumber
nested_params.description: A number identifying the part in a read set upload.

nested_params.name: partSource
nested_params.description: The source file of the part being uploaded.

nested_params.name: checksum
nested_params.description: A unique identifier used to confirm that parts are being added to the correct upload.

nested_items.name: readSetId
nested_items.description: The read set ID created for an uploaded read set.
